






@(1 = 1-8) The heroic @wDN{Nanna-Suen} fixed his mind on the city of his mother. @wDN{Suen} @wDN{Ašimbabbar} fixed his mind on the city of his mother. @wDN{Nanna-Suen} fixed his mind on the city of his mother and his father. @wDN{Ašimbabbar} fixed his mind on the city of @wDN{Enlil} and @wDN{Ninlil}:

@(9 = 9-16) @q[Nanna-Suen,self]{“I, the hero, will set off for my city. I will set off for my city, I will set off to my father. I, @wDN{Suen}, will set off for my city. I will set off for my city, I will set off to my father. I will set off to my father @wDN{Enlil}. I will set off for my city, I will set off to my mother. I will set off to my mother @wDN{Ninlil}. I will set off to my father.”}

