…… very great, …… very great, …… very great, …… very great.”}

@(28 = 28-36) @q{“My @wSN{Nibru}, where black birch trees grow in a good place, my sanctuary @wSN{Nibru}, where white birch trees grow in a pure place -- my @wSN{Nibru's} shrine is built in a good place. The sanctuary @wSN{Nibru's} name is a good name. My @wSN{Nibru's} shrine is built in a good place. The sanctuary @wSN{Nibru's} name is a good name. Before @wSN{Dilmun} existed, palm trees grew in my city. Before @wSN{Dilmun} existed, palm trees grew in @wSN{Nibru} and the great mother @wDN{Ninlil} was clothed in fine linen.”}


